2023.1
    Updated dependencies versions on Test::Harness and Test::Simple. They changed output, providing exit codes. This was
    failing tests during installation.

2021.1
    Fixed problem with false-positive result on non-zero exiting without failed tests. NB: error messages sticks to the
     previous test or warning because there is no explicit test finished event.

